{"tid":1989501,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普缺席疫情記者會 斥媒體惡意提問","createTime":"2020-04-26T04:30:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T06:13:35.000Z","uid":66087,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f3274e09ad736e1434ccfc616487cfd55da01348","tid":1989501,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:30:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/特朗普缺席疫情記者會-斥媒體惡意提問-分析指頻出錯憂損選情/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E7%BC%BA%E5%B8%AD%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%9C%83-%E6%96%A5%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E6%83%A1%E6%84%8F%E6%8F%90%E5%95%8F-%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E6%8C%87%E9%A0%BB%E5%87%BA%E9%8C%AF%E6%86%82%E6%90%8D%E9%81%B8%E6%83%85%2F&d=lW7zubw4D25L16l94wxnCvtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=2ee3e05d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E7%BC%BA%E5%B8%AD%E7%96%AB%E6%83%85%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E6%9C%83-%E6%96%A5%E5%AA%92%E9%AB%94%E6%83%A1%E6%84%8F%E6%8F%90%E5%95%8F-%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E6%8C%87%E9%A0%BB%E5%87%BA%E9%8C%AF%E6%86%82%E6%90%8D%E9%81%B8%E6%83%85%2F&h=0346c1bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/特朗普缺席疫情記者會-斥媒體惡意提問-分析指頻出錯憂損選情/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國白宮取消了當地星期六（25日）的每日疫情記者會。總統特朗普在Twitter社交專頁說，媒體盡是惡意提問，出席記者會根本沒意思。不過，多家美國媒體分析指，共和黨擔心特朗普日日在記者會上發言，有損他的公信力，甚至危害他連任的選情。<br />\n<br />\n媒體 The Politico 指，特朗普主持疫情匯報頻頻出錯，星期四更指可以注射消毒劑入人體作為治療新型肺炎，其持續發表沒有醫學根據的言論令國際譁然，醫療專家以至清潔劑生產商都對他作出抨擊。<br />\n<br />\n近數星期的民調數字顯示，民眾對他處理疫症的表現評分下跌，其身邊幕僚曾建議他縮短講話時間，讓醫療專家回應記者提問。"},{"pid":"5ffcc8916eee94e9675f51beb91e2960818b4f12","tid":1989501,"uid":66087,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T04:31:19.000Z","msg":"所有記者都係仆街，係咁攻擊侵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一怕兩散 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac